| Age group | Govt. | Pvt. | Other | Not in school | Total |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Age 6-14: All | 40.2 | 52.1 | 2.4 | 5.3 | 100 |
| Age 7-16: All | 37.2 | 52.2 | 2.1 | 8.4 | 100 |
