| Age 11-14: Girls | 38.9 | 49.2 | 2.0 | 9.9 | 100 |
| Age 15-16: All | 27.0 | 50.3 | 1.1 | 21.6 | 100 |
| Age 15-16: Boys | 27.3 | 53.2 | 1.0 | 18.5 | 100 |
